blurbs.title: Webmiddle
blurbs.text: Node.js framework for extracting and transforming web resources. Webmiddle applications can range from simple web scrapers to complex web integration tools targeting JSON APIs, raw HTML pages, XML resources and so on.

blurbs.title: Backbone Debugger
blurbs.text: Chrome Developer Tools extension for debugging Backbone.js applications.
